{"label":"Let's Speak","id":"conversation-4","lockAfter":2,"list":[{"id":"grammar","type":"passage","label":"Grammar Class","data":{"title":"Grammar Class","text":[{"type":"html","text":"<b>Teacher</b>: Mona, sand up. What am I teaching?<br>\n<b>Mona</b>: Sir, you are teaching grammar.<br>\n<b>Teacher</b>: Mona, look at the board. See the word - Adjective! Is the spelling correct?<br>\n<b>Mona</b>: Yes, Sir. The spelling is correct.<br>\n<b>Teacher</b>: Can anyone tell me what a noun is?<br>\n<b>Riya</b>: A noun is the name of a person, a place or a thing.<br>\n<b>Teacher</b>: Delhi is the capital city of India. Name any two nouns used in this sentence.<br>\n<b>Riya</b>: Delhi and the city are the two nouns.<br>\n<b>Teacher</b>: What kind of nouns are they?<br>\n<b>Peter</b>: Delhi is a proper noun and the city is a common noun."}]}},{"id":"career","type":"passage","label":"Career","data":{"title":"Career","text":[{"type":"html","text":"<b>Father</b>: Now that you have appeared for the Class XII exams, what are your plans for the future?<br>\n<b>Son</b>: I have yet to decide. I think I'll join some college.<br> \n<b>Father</b>: Don't you feel that by now you should have decided your goal in life?<br>\n<b>Son</b>: My ultimate goal is to become a cricket player.<br>\n<b>Father</b>: It's too late now. Have you ever played for your school team?<br>\n<b>Son</b>: I have played thrice.<br>\n<b>Father</b>: Well! If you were not a member of your school team you should forget about cricket.<br>\n<b>Son</b>: But father, I love cricket, I cannot stop playing it.<br>\n<b>Father</b>: You are a grown-up boy. Be serious and decide on a suitable career for yourself.<br>\n<b>Son</b>: I will think again but I cannot promise."}]}},{"id":"ticket","type":"passage","label":"Ticket Reservation","data":{"title":"Ticket Reservation","text":[{"type":"html","text":"<b>Clerk</b>: Good morning! How may I help you?<br>\n<b>Passenger</b>: I want a reservation of two tickets to Delhi.<br>\n<b>Clerk</b>: Have you filled out the reservation form?<br>\n<b>Passenger</b>: Here it is!<br>\n<b>Clerk</b>: But there is no seat available on 25th January.<br>\n<b>Passenger</b>: Is there any seat available in Jan Shatabdi Express?<br>\n<b>Clerk</b>: Yes. There are two seats available in Jan Shatabdi Express.<br>\n<b>Passenger</b>: What is the time of departure?<br>\n<b>Clerk</b>: The time of departure is 07:38 am.<br>\n<b>Passenger</b>: Please book two tickets. Thank you, Sir."}]}},{"id":"gift","type":"passage","label":"At the Gift Shop","data":{"title":"At the Gift Shop","text":[{"type":"html","text":"<b>Customer</b>: Good morning! I'm looking for a gift for my friend's birthday. Can you help me find something unique and special?<br>\n<b>Shopkeeper</b>: Good morning! Of course, I'd be happy to assist you. What kind of gift are you thinking of? Does your friend have any specific interests or hobbies?<br>\n<b>Customer</b>: Well, my friend loves cooking and experimenting with new recipes. I was thinking of getting something related to that.<br>\n<b>Shopkeeper</b>: That's a great idea! We have a variety of kitchen gadgets and cookware that could be perfect. How about a high-quality chef's knife set? It's an essential tool for any aspiring chef.<br>\n<b>Customer</b>: That sounds like a fantastic gift! Do you have any recommendations for a specific brand or style?<br>\n<b>Shopkeeper</b>: I would recommend our top-selling stainless steel knife set. It's known for its durability and precision. It also comes with a beautiful wooden knife block for easy storage.<br>\n<b>Customer</b>: That sounds perfect! I think my friend will love it. Can you show me the set?<br>\n<b>Shopkeeper</b>: Absolutely! Let me bring it out for you. Here it is. As you can see, the knives have a comfortable grip and a sharp edge. They're also dishwasher safe, which makes cleaning them a breeze.<br>\n<b>Customer</b>: I'm really impressed with the quality and design. This is exactly what I was looking for. How much does it cost?<br>\n<b>Shopkeeper</b>: The set is priced at Rs.499.99. It's an excellent value for the quality and functionality it offers.<br>\n<b>Customer</b>: That's within my budget. I'll take it! Can you help me with the gift wrapping?<br>\n<b>Shopkeeper</b>: Of course! We provide a complimentary gift-wrapping service. I'll make sure it looks beautiful for your friend's special day.<br>\n<b>Customer</b>: Thank you so much for your assistance. I really appreciate it!<br>\n<b>Shopkeeper</b>: You're welcome! It was my pleasure to help. I hope your friend enjoys the gift. If you need any more assistance, feel free to ask. Have a wonderful day!"}]}},{"id":"loan","type":"passage","label":"Educational Loan","data":{"title":"Educational Loan","text":[{"type":"html","text":"<b>Student</b>: Good morning, sir. I hope you're doing well. I'm here to inquire about an education loan for my higher studies.<br>\n<b>Bank Manager</b>: Good morning! I'm glad you're considering a loan for your education. Please have a seat. I'll be happy to assist you. Could you please provide me with some details?<br>\n<b>Student</b>: Thank you, sir. I'm pursuing a bachelor's degree in computer science and I'm in my final year. I have been accepted into a prestigious university for a master's program in artificial intelligence. The total cost of the program is quite high, and I'm in need of financial assistance to cover my tuition fees and living expenses.<br>\n<b>Bank Manager</b>: That sounds like an excellent opportunity for you. We understand the importance of education and are here to support you. Could you please provide me with the necessary documents, such as your admission letter, academic records, and a breakdown of the program's expenses?<br>\n<b>Student</b>: Certainly, sir. I have all those documents ready. Here they are.<br>\n<b>Bank Manager</b>: Thank you. I will review these documents and assess your eligibility for the loan. Additionally, I will also consider your academic performance and potential job prospects after completing your studies. We offer competitive interest rates and flexible repayment options for education loans.<br>\n<b>Student</b>: That's great to hear, sir. I have a good academic record and plan to work in the field of artificial intelligence after graduation. I'm confident that I can repay the loan in a timely manner.<br>\n<b>Bank Manager</b>: That's commendable. We value your determination and will do our best to support you. Once I've reviewed your application, I will contact you with the loan offer and further details. Is there anything else you would like to know?<br>\n<b>Student</b>: No, sir. You have answered all my questions. Thank you for your time and assistance.<br>\n<b>Bank Manager</b>: You're welcome! I wish you the best of luck with your studies and future career. We look forward to helping you achieve your educational goals. Feel free to reach out if you have any further queries. Have a great day!"}]}},{"id":"train","type":"passage","label":"Train Ride","data":{"title":"Train Ride","text":[{"type":"html","text":"<b>Conductor</b>: Good morning, ma'am. May I see your ticket, please?<br>\n<b>Passenger</b>: Good morning. Of course, here it is.<br>\n<b>Conductor</b>: Thank you. I see you're traveling to New York. Have you been on this train before?<br>\n<b>Passenger</b>: No, it's my first time. I'm excited about the journey.<br>\n<b>Conductor</b>: That's great to hear! This train offers a smooth ride and beautiful views along the way. If you have any questions or need assistance during the journey, feel free to ask.<br>\n<b>Passenger</b>: Thank you. I appreciate it. Could you let me know when we'll be arriving in New York?<br>\n<b>Conductor</b>: Certainly. We're scheduled to arrive in New York at 11:30 a.m. local time. However, please keep in mind that delays can occur due to unforeseen circumstances. I'll make announcements if there are any changes to the schedule.<br>\n<b>Passenger</b>: Understood. I'll keep an eye out for any updates. Is there a dining car on this train?<br>\n<b>Conductor</b>: Yes, we do have a dining car located two cars down from here. They serve breakfast until 10:00 a.m. and offer a variety of meals throughout the journey. I recommend trying their famous omelettes.<br> \n<b>Passenger</b>: That sounds delicious. I'll make sure to visit the dining car before they stop serving breakfast. Thank you for the information.<br>\n<b>Conductor</b>: You're welcome. If you need anything else, don't hesitate to ask. Enjoy your journey, and let me know if there's anything I can assist you with.<br>\n<b>Passenger</b>: Thank you for your help. I'm looking forward to the trip."}]}},{"id":"hospital","type":"passage","label":"At the Hospital","data":{"title":"At the Hospital","text":[{"type":"html","text":"<b>Doctor</b>: Good morning! How can I assist you today?<br>\n<b>Patient</b>: Good morning, Doctor. I've been experiencing persistent headaches and occasional dizziness for the past week. It's starting to worry me.<br>\n<b>Doctor</b>: I understand your concern. Let's start by discussing your symptoms in detail. Have you noticed any triggers for your headaches or any specific patterns?<br>\n<b>Patient</b>: I haven't noticed any specific triggers. The headaches usually occur in the afternoon and can last for a few hours. The dizziness comes and goes, but it's not constant.<br>\n<b>Doctor</b>: I see. Based on your symptoms, I'd like to rule out any underlying causes. Have you had any recent head injuries or changes in your medication?<br>\n<b>Patient</b>: No, I haven't had any head injuries, and I'm not taking any new medications. My overall health has been good until now.<br>\n<b>Doctor</b>: All right. In order to reach a diagnosis, I recommend conducting some tests. We'll start with a comprehensive blood test to check for any potential imbalances or deficiencies. We may also consider a brain imaging scan if necessary.<br>\n<b>Patient</b>: That sounds reasonable. I just want to find out what's causing these symptoms.<br>\n<b>Doctor</b>: I understand. Let's proceed with the blood tests first. In the meantime, I recommend keeping a journal of your symptoms, noting the time, duration, and any possible triggers. This information will be valuable during our next visit.<br>\n<b>Patient</b>: Thank you, Doctor. I'll make sure to keep track of everything. I appreciate your help.<br>\n<b>Doctor</b>: You're welcome. Remember, it's important not to worry too much before we have more information. We'll work together to find the cause and develop a suitable treatment plan. I'll see you again soon for the test results, and we'll take it from there.<br>\n<b>Patient</b>: Thank you, Doctor. I feel reassured knowing that we're taking the necessary steps to uncover the cause. I'll see you soon.<br>\n<b>Doctor</b>: Take care, and I'll see you soon. Don't hesitate to contact the clinic if you have any urgent concerns before our next appointment."}]}},{"id":"principal","type":"passage","label":"At the Principal's Office","data":{"title":"At the Principal's Office","text":[{"type":"html","text":"<b>Principal</b>: Good morning, Mr. Johnson. Thank you for coming in today. Please have a seat.<br>\n<b>Parent</b>: Good morning, Principal Johnson. It's a pleasure to meet with you. Thank you for taking the time to see me.<br>\n<b>Principal</b>: Of course, it's my pleasure. How can I assist you today?<br>\n<b>Parent</b>: I wanted to discuss my child's recent academic performance. I've noticed a decline in their grades, and I'm concerned about their progress.<br>\n<b>Principal</b>: I understand your concerns. We've also noticed a drop in your child's grades. We've been monitoring their progress closely and have been providing additional support through tutoring and study groups.<br>\n<b>Parent</b>: I appreciate the extra support. Is there anything else we can do at home to help improve their performance?<br>\n<b>Principal</b>: Regular communication with <b>Teacher</b>s is crucial. Stay engaged with their homework assignments and ensure they have a quiet space to study. Encourage a consistent routine and emphasize the importance of completing tasks on time.<br>\n<b>Parent</b>: That's helpful advice. I'll make sure we implement those strategies at home. Additionally, my child has expressed some concerns about bullying. Can you please address this issue?<br>\n<b>Principal</b>: I'm sorry to hear that your child is experiencing bullying. We take such matters very seriously. I assure you that we have protocols in place to address bullying incidents. We will investigate the matter thoroughly and take appropriate action.<br>\n<b>Parent</b>: Thank you for your attention to this matter, Principal Johnson. I appreciate your commitment to the safety and well-being of all students.<br>\n<b>Principal</b>: You're welcome. It's our duty to provide a safe and supportive learning environment. If you have any other concerns or questions, please don't hesitate to reach out to me or our staff. Together, we can ensure your child's success.<br>\n<b>Parent</b>: Thank you, Principal Johnson. I appreciate your time and willingness to address these concerns."}]}},{"id":"dog","type":"passage","label":"Cat and Dog","data":{"title":"Cat and Dog","text":[{"type":"html","text":"<b>Cat</b>: Hey there, Dog! How's your day going?<br>\n<b>Dog</b>: Oh, hello, Cat! My day has been pawsome, as always! I've been playing fetch with my human in the park. What about you?<br>\n<b>Cat</b>: That sounds like fun! Well, you know me, I've been napping most of the day, basking in the warm sunbeam by the window. Life of a cat, you know.<br>\n<b>Dog</b>: Ah, the life of leisure! I envy you sometimes. But I must say, chasing balls and going for walks with my human fills me with so much joy. Have you ever tried fetching?<br>\n<b>Cat</b>: Fetching? No, that's more of a dog thing. I prefer to observe the world from my perch and gracefully pounce on my toys. Different strokes for different folks, right?<br>\n<b>Dog</b>: Absolutely, Cat! We all have our unique ways of enjoying life. But you should give fetching a try sometime. It's a great way to bond with your humans and get some exercise too.<br>\n<b>Cat</b>: Hmm, maybe I'll consider it. But for now, I'll stick to my napping routine. Speaking of routines, I hear you have a knack for tricks. Any new ones to show off?<br>\n<b>Dog</b>: Oh, you bet! I've been learning some new tricks like rolling over and giving high-fives. My humans are always impressed. They say I'm a smart dog, you know.<br>\n<b>Cat</b>: Impressive indeed! Maybe I'll learn a few tricks of my own someday. But for now, let's just enjoy being our unique selves, and maybe I'll join you for a walk in the park sometime."}]}},{"id":"coach","type":"passage","label":"Coach","data":{"title":"Coach","text":[{"type":"html","text":"<b>Coach</b>: Hey, player! How are you feeling today?<br>\n<b>Player</b>: I'm doing well, coach. Ready to give it my all in today's practice.<br>\n<b>Coach</b>: That's the spirit! I've noticed some areas where we can improve your performance. Let's focus on your dribbling skills today. I want you to work on maintaining control while changing directions quickly.<br>\n<b>Player</b>: Sounds good, coach. I've been practicing my dribbling, but I know there's always room for improvement.<br>\n<b>Coach</b>: That's the attitude I like to hear. Remember, it's all about discipline and consistency. I want you to push yourself beyond your comfort zone during the drills today.<br>\n<b>Player</b>: I'm up for the challenge, coach. I want to become the best player I can be.<br>\n<b>Coach</b>: Excellent! I'll be closely observing your technique and footwork. If I notice any areas that need adjustment, I'll provide you with constructive feedback to help you grow.<br>\n<b>Player</b>: I appreciate that, coach. Your guidance has always been valuable to me.<br>\n<b>Coach</b>: It's my job to help you reach your full potential. Together, we'll work on refining your skills and elevating your game. Trust the process, and let's make every practice count.<br>\n<b>Player</b>: Absolutely, coach. I'm ready to put in the hard work and make progress. I won't let you down.<br>\n<b>Coach</b>: I know you won't. Stay focused, stay determined, and give it your all. I believe in you, player.<br>\n<b>Player</b>: Thanks, coach. With your support, I'm confident I can become a stronger player. Let's make it happen!"}]}},{"id":"dream","type":"passage","label":"Dream","data":{"title":"Dream","text":[{"type":"html","text":"<b>Mother</b>: Good morning, sweetheart! How did you sleep last night?<br>\n<b>Daughter</b>: Good morning, Mom! I slept well, thank you. I had the strangest dream though. It felt so real!<br>\n<b>Mother</b>: Oh, really? Tell me all about it. Dreams can be so fascinating.<br>\n<b>Daughter</b>: Well, I dreamt that I was exploring a magical forest with talking animals. It was like something out of a fairytale!<br>\n<b>Mother</b>: Wow, that sounds incredible. What did you see in this magical forest?<br>\n<b>Daughter</b>: Colorful butterflies were fluttering around, and I even had a conversation with a wise old owl. It was so magical and surreal.<br>\n<b>Mother</b>: That sounds absolutely enchanting! Dreams have a way of taking us to places we could never imagine. What did you learn from the owl?<br>\n<b>Daughter</b>: The owl told me to always trust my instincts and follow my heart. It said that I have the power to achieve anything I set my mind to. It was such an inspiring message.<br>\n<b>Mother</b>: That's a beautiful lesson, sweetheart. You truly have a vivid imagination. Remember, dreams can sometimes reflect our inner desires and aspirations. Keep believing in yourself and never be afraid to pursue your dreams.<br>\n<b>Daughter</b>: Thank you, Mom. I'll always remember the wise owl's advice. I'm so grateful to have you as my mom, supporting me every step of the way.<br>\n<b>Mother</b>: And I'm grateful to have such a wonderful daughter like you. Let's make today a special day filled with love, laughter, and the pursuit of our dreams. I'm here for you, always.<br>\n<b>Daughter</b>: I love you, Mom.<br>\n<b>Mother</b>: I love you too, my dear. Now, let's start the day with a smile and make the most of every moment together."}]}},{"id":"sports","type":"passage","label":"Importance of Sports","data":{"title":"Importance of Sports","text":[{"type":"html","text":"<b>Peter</b>: Hey, have you ever thought about how important sports are in our lives?<br>\n<b>John</b>: Yeah, definitely! I believe sports play a crucial role in our overall development. They aren't just about physical activity; they offer numerous benefits.<br>\n<b>Peter</b>: Absolutely! One obvious advantage is improved physical health. Regular sports participation keeps our bodies fit, increases stamina, and helps prevent many health issues.<br>\n<b>John</b>: True, but it's not just about the body. Sports also have a positive impact on our mental health. They reduce stress, boost our mood, and improve our self-esteem.<br>\n<b>Peter</b>: You're right! Plus, sports teach us essential life skills, like teamwork, leadership, discipline, and time management. These skills are valuable in both personal and professional life.<br>\n<b>John</b>: Exactly! And let's not forget about the sense of camaraderie and friendship that sports foster. It brings people from diverse backgrounds together, promoting social interaction and cultural exchange.<br>\n<b>Peter</b>: Plus, in schools, sports help in academic performance too. Research shows that students who participate in sports tend to have better focus, concentration, and overall academic achievement.<br>\n<b>John</b>: That's an essential point! It keeps students engaged and motivated in their studies.<br>\n<b>Peter</b>: And beyond schools, sports play a significant role in building national pride and unity. Look at how major sporting events bring a country together, fostering a sense of belonging.<br>\n<b>John</b>: You're absolutely right! So, considering all these benefits, I think it's essential to encourage everyone, especially young people, to participate actively in sports.<br>\n<b>Peter</b>: I couldn't agree more! Whether it's for recreational purposes or competitive sports, the importance of sports in our lives cannot be underestimated. It's a win-win situation for everyone."}]}},{"id":"park","type":"passage","label":"A Day at the Park","data":{"title":"A Day at the Park","text":[{"type":"html","text":"[At a beautiful park on a sunny day, Alex, Ben, Chloe, and Diana sit on a blanket, enjoying the pleasant weather.]<br><br>\n<b>Alex</b>: (excitedly) What a perfect day to be outdoors! I'm so glad we decided to come to the park.<br>\n<b>Ben</b>: (nodding) Absolutely! It's been ages since we all hung out together like this.<br>\n<b>Chloe</b>: (smiling) I agree. Life gets so busy sometimes; we should do this more often.<br>\n<b>Diana</b>: (unpacking snacks) Speaking of which, who's up for some sandwiches?<br>\n<b>Alex</b>: (grinning) Count me in! By the way, has anyone seen that new movie everyone's talking about?<br>\n<b>Ben</b>: (nodding) Yes, I caught it last week. It was fantastic! We should plan a movie night soon.<br>\n<b>Chloe</b>: (pointing to a nearby lake) Oh, look at those ducks! They're so adorable.<br>\n<b>Diana</b>: (joining Chloe) They really are. Hey, remember that trip we took last year and saw swans in the lake?<br>\n<b>Alex</b>: (laughing) How could we forget! That was such a hilarious and unforgettable adventure.<br>\n<b>Ben</b>: (leaning back) Life was so much simpler back then. But you know what? I'm grateful for the memories we've made together.<br>\n<b>Chloe</b>: (sincerely) Me too. Friends like you all make life brighter.<br>\n<b>Diana</b>: (raising her drink) Cheers to that!<br><br>\n[They clink their glasses together, savoring the moment of friendship.]<br><br>\n<b>Alex</b>: (contently) Let's promise to keep these moments alive, no matter how busy life gets.<br>\n<b>Ben</b>: (agreeing) Absolutely. We'll plan more outings, movie nights, and adventures. Our friendship is too precious not to cherish.<br>\n<b>Chloe</b>: (smiling) Agreed. Now, who's up for a game of Frisbee?<br>\n<b>Diana</b>: (playfully) Bring it on! This day just keeps getting better!<br><br>\n[As they continue their day at the park, laughter and joy fill the air, making it a day to remember for the four friends.]"}]}},{"id":"meeting","type":"passage","label":"Parent-Teacher Meeting","data":{"title":"Parent-Teacher Meeting","text":[{"type":"html","text":"<b>Parent</b>: Good morning, Mrs. Johnson. I wanted to schedule a meeting to discuss my child's progress in your class.<br>\n<b>Teacher</b>: Good morning, Mr. Thompson. Of course, I'm glad you reached out. I've noticed some great improvements in your child's academic performance.<br>\n<b>Parent</b>: That's wonderful to hear! Could you please provide more details about their progress? I want to understand how they are doing in different subjects.<br>\n<b>Teacher</b>: Certainly. In mathematics, your child has been consistently scoring high marks and actively participating in class discussions. They have also shown significant improvement in their writing skills and have been taking initiative in completing assignments on time. However, I've noticed they're struggling a bit in science. It might be helpful to provide some extra support in that area.<br>\n<b>Parent</b>: Thank you for the detailed update. I appreciate your efforts in helping my child excel. Regarding science, what specific areas do they need assistance with?<br>\n<b>Teacher</b>: They seem to be having difficulty understanding certain scientific concepts, especially in the area of chemistry. I suggest reviewing the periodic table and chemical reactions with them at home. Additionally, encouraging them to ask questions in class and seeking additional resources online might also be beneficial.<br>\n<b>Parent</b>: I will definitely work on those areas with my child. Are there any upcoming assignments or projects I should be aware of to provide further support?<br>\n<b>Teacher</b>: We have a group project coming up next week that focuses on teamwork and research skills. It would be great if you could guide your child in selecting a suitable topic and encourage them to work effectively with their teammates.<br>\n<b>Parent</b>: I'll make sure to provide the necessary guidance and support. Thank you for keeping me informed about my child's progress and providing valuable recommendations. I really appreciate your dedication.<br>\n<b>Teacher</b>: You're welcome, Mr. Thompson. It's my pleasure to work with your child. Let's continue to stay in touch and collaborate for their academic growth."}]}},{"id":"old-friend","type":"passage","label":"Meeting an Old Friend","data":{"title":"Meeting an Old Friend","text":[{"type":"html","text":"<b>Sara</b>: Hey, it's been so long since we last hung out! How have you been?<br>\n<b>Mary</b>: I know, right? I've missed you! I've been doing pretty well. Life has been keeping me busy with work and other commitments. How about you?<br>\n<b>Sara</b>: Oh, I can relate. Work has been hectic for me too. But apart from that, everything's been great. I recently picked up a new hobby - painting. It's been a wonderful creative outlet for me.<br>\n<b>Mary</b>: That's awesome! I always admired your artistic side. We should plan a painting session together sometime. I'd love to learn from you.<br>\n<b>Sara</b>: Definitely! I'd be thrilled to share my passion with you. By the way, have you seen any good movies or read any interesting books lately?<br>\n<b>Mary</b>: Oh, yes! I watched this incredible sci-fi movie last week. The visuals were mind-blowing, and the storyline had so many unexpected twists. It kept me on the edge of my seat the entire time. I highly recommend it.<br>\n<b>Sara</b>: Sounds intriguing! I'm a huge fan of sci-fi, so I'll definitely check it out. As for books, I recently finished this gripping mystery novel. The author's writing style was fantastic, and the suspense had me hooked from start to finish.<br>\n<b>Mary</b>: Wow, that sounds like my kind of book. Could you lend it to me? I'm always on the lookout for thrilling reads.<br>\n<b>Sara</b>: Of course! I'll bring it the next time we meet. We should plan a movie and book exchange session soon. It'll be so much fun.<br>\n<b>Mary</b>: Absolutely! I can't wait. We always have the best discussions about movies and books. It's one of the things I love most about our friendship.<br>\n<b>Sara</b>: Same here. It's great to have someone who shares similar interests and with whom I can have meaningful conversations."}]}}]}